[0.019, "o", "\u001b[0;1;32m●\u001b[0m mariadb.service - MariaDB 12.3.2 database server\r\n     Loaded: loaded (\u001b]8;;file://tya/usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service\u001b\\/usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service\u001b]8;;\u001b\\; \u001b[0;1;32menabled\u001b[0m; preset: \u001b[0;1;33m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185mdisabled\u001b[0m)\r\n    Drop-In: /usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service.d\r\n             └─\u001b]8;;file://tya/usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service.d/galera.conf\u001b\\galera.conf\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n     Active: \u001b[0;1;32mactive (running)\u001b[0m since Sun 2026-06-07 17:12:10 WIB; 10s ago\r\n Invocation: d8d4c9a82e524cb0ab7c132df5c3def6\r\n       Docs: \u001b]8;;man:mariadbd(8)\u001b\\man:mariadbd(8)\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n             \u001b]8;;https://mariadb.com/kb/en/library/systemd/\u001b\\https://mariadb.com/kb/en/library/systemd/\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n    Process: 1668 ExecStartPre=/bin/sh -c [ ! -e /usr/bin/galera_recovery ] && VAR= ||   VAR=`/usr/bin/galera_recovery`; [ $? -eq 0 ]   && echo _WSREP_START_POSITION=$VAR > /run/mariadb/wsrep-start-position || exit 1 (code=exited, status=0/SUCCESS)\r\n    Process: 1709 ExecStartPost=/bin/rm -f /run/mariadb/wsrep-start-position /run/mariadb/wsrep-new-cluster (code=exited, status=0/SUCCESS)\r\n   Main PID: 1693 (mariadbd)\r\n     Status: \"\u001b[0;1;36mTaking your SQL requests now...\u001b[0m\"\r\n      Tasks: 15\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m (limit: 93108)\u001b[0m\r\n     Memory: 96M (peak: 98.2M)\r\n        CPU: 766ms\r\n     CGroup: /system.slice/mariadb.service\r\n             └─\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m1693 /usr/bin/mariadbd\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nJun 07 17:12:10 tya mariadbd[1693]: 2026-06-07 17:12:10 0 [Note] InnoDB: log sequence number 45434; transaction id 15\r\nJun 07 17:12:10 tya mariadbd[1693]: 2026-06-07 17:12:10 0 [Note] InnoDB: Loading buffer pool(s) from /var/lib/mysql/ib_buffer_pool\r\nJun 07 17:12:10 tya mariadbd[1693]: 2026-06-07 17:12:10 0 [Note] Plugin 'wsrep-provider' is disabled.\r\nJun 07 17:12:10 tya mariadbd[1693]: 2026-06-07 17:12:10 0 [Note] InnoDB: Buffer pool(s) load completed at 260607 17:12:10\r\nJun 07 17:12:10 tya mariadbd[1693]: 2026-06-07 17:12:10 0 [Note] Server socket created on IP: '0.0.0.0', port: '3306'.\r\nJun 07 17:12:10 tya mariadbd[1693]: 2026-06-07 17:12:10 0 [Note] Server socket created on IP: '::', port: '3306'.\r\nJun 07 17:12:10 tya mariadbd[1693]: 2026-06-07 17:12:10 0 [Note] mariadbd: Event Scheduler: Loaded 0 events\r\nJun 07 17:12:10 tya mariadbd[1693]: 2026-06-07 17:12:10 0 [Note] /usr/bin/mariadbd: ready for connections.\r\nJun 07 17:12:10 tya mariadbd[1693]: Version: '12.3.2-MariaDB'  socket: '/run/mysqld/mysqld.sock'  port: 3306  Arch Linux\r\nJun 07 17:12:10 tya systemd[1]: Started MariaDB 12.3.2 database server.\r\n"]
